3212	  Let \(M\) be a sheaf of \(R\)-modules and \(\{X_i\}\) an indexed family of objects of the site with
3213	  \(\mathrm{CoversTop}\,\{X_i\}\). If the Grothendieck-slice restriction \(M.\mathrm{over}\,X_i\) is
